<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/newsflashes/933934454245766">苏州成为全国率先提供无人公交服务的城市</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373523" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/006Fd7o3gy1gjml0vli0ej30rs0fm1kx.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="562" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/006Fd7o3gy1gjml0vli0ej30rs0fm1kx.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/006Fd7o3gy1gjml0vli0ej30rs0fm1kx-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/006Fd7o3gy1gjml0vli0ej30rs0fm1kx-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>昨天，中国移动 5G 自动驾驶峰会期间，全国首个常态化运营 5G 无人公交亮相苏州，该项目由无人驾驶公司轻舟智航和中国移动联合部署。</p>
<p>同期，「苏州无人公交早鸟计划」启动招募，计划招募第一批有日常通勤需求的普通市民，免费搭乘无人公交。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5145522.html">西贝开出首家卖「半成品菜」的餐厅</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373524" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/160325785551265600_a700xH.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="555" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/160325785551265600_a700xH.jpeg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/160325785551265600_a700xH-360x285.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，西贝旗下专做半成品菜的「贾国龙功夫菜」在北京开出首个门店。</p>
<p>店内销售的所有菜品均为半成品，包括西北菜、八大菜系等 30 多个 SKU，它们被放在冷冻保鲜柜里，当顾客下单后，店员会将其加热然后送上餐桌。</p>
<p>此前，「贾国龙功夫菜」已经在盒马、小程序和电商平台上销售。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>多家银行已提前终止 785 款理财产品</h4>
<p>近期，有一些投资者接到了银行的通知，说自己购买的理财产品，明明合约没有到期，却被提前终止。</p>
<p>今年以来，提前终止的银行理财产品已有 785 款。业内人士表示，银行提前终止部分理财产品 ，有一个很重要的原因就是资管新规。</p>
<p>网友：「消费者想要提前终止不可以，银行就可以了？」「之前我爸去银行存钱，然后第二天发短信说成保险了！幸亏发现得早及时去找银行退了……」「规范化管理很必要。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/949528/zhong-fang-ji-ge-zhe-zhi-jia-a-lai-fu-shi-kong-yan-jiu-suo">众方纪 @ 额尔古纳·中国</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373295" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7-2.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7-2-360x288.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7-2-1024x819.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>民谣歌手陈鸿宇小时候在读《鲁滨逊漂流记》时萌生了一个想法，希望能在从小生活的土地上建一座「诺亚方舟」。于是，他邀请工作室「阿莱夫时空研究所」为其设计了一座住宅「众方纪」。</p>
<p>设计遵循了一个立面只开一扇景观窗的逻辑，每扇窗都有自己「风景」的设定。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373299" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/10-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/10-2.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/10-2-360x288.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/10-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/10-2-1024x819.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>餐厅的窗户向西，晚餐时可看夕阳；工作室的窗户向北，光线均匀无直射光；楼梯间的窗户向东，看向父母的住宅与牛棚；卫生间的窗户则为天窗。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373302" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="811" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind-360x146.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind-768x311.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wind-1024x415.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>室内空间被分别在 XYZ 轴上的三刀切成 8 个长宽高各 3m 的空间。二楼的四个房间通过其中心交点的一个旋转门所连接，可根据不同的时间的不同场景开关。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1373301" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/23.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/23.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/23-360x288.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/23-768x614.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/23-1024x819.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>陈鸿宇常居外地，众方纪开始开放免费驻留，申请者将进行 72 小时的无时间提示的独处。</p>